Monitoring Windows Containers

Monitoring Windows Containers Application requires running collectors on each docker host. Please follow documentation of collector to learn how to configure Docker hosts.

Collector is a Proprietary Software with trial period of 30 days. Contact sales@outcoldsolutions.com to request a quote and purchase the license, or if you need to extend trial period.

For any technical difficulties contact support@outcoldsolutions.com.

For documentation, see: https://www.outcoldsolutions.com

